{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 ReaImGui: ReaScript binding for Dear ImGui\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ReaImGui is a ReaScript binding for the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.dearimgui.org/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Dear ImGui
}}}
 toolkit. It adds over 300 ReaScript API functions (over 600 including constants!) for creating GPU-rendered GUI interfaces.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 See Dear ImGui's {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.dearimgui.org/faq/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
FAQ
}}}
.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Contributing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Send bug reports on the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/cfillion/reaimgui/issues"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
issue tracker
}}}
. The source code is provided under LGPLv3 on {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/cfillion/reaimgui"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
GitHub
}}}
. Patches can be submitted as pull requests.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A REAPER extension to emulate digital console type of workflow for setting channelstrip plugin parameters in the context of currently selected track/channel. Registers 32 custom actions which function as kind of API based virtual control surface, or 'dynamic' macro controls similar to Quick Controls in Cubase. 8 endless rotary encoders in MIDI Relative mode and 24 buttons are supported, and in practice required for any reasonable use. 8 buttons are reserved for navigating the 'virtual channelstrip'. Built-in support for some FabFilters, the ReEQ and some stock REAPER plugins. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/ak5k/reafab"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
More information on GitHub
}}}
\par}
}

